        <p><strong>Accepted Quote</strong> means any quote, proposal, pricing page, online checkout, order summary or similar document or interface issued or made available by us and accepted by you by signature, click-through acceptance, email confirmation, payment, or other written or electronic acceptance method approved by us.</p>
