        <p><strong>Fees</strong> means all fees, charges and amounts payable by you under this Agreement, including subscription fees, setup fees, implementation fees, development fees, support fees and any other fees specified in an Order, Accepted Quote, statement of work, Account or on the Site.</p>
        <p><strong>Services</strong> means the hosted software-as-a-service products, features, functionality, support, hosting, implementation, setup and related services provided by us under this Agreement, including PlaceOS One and any agreed modules, features or related services.</p>

